description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Federal Republic of Germany / Bremen Market Square
-United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland / Changing the Guard at Buckingham Palace
-French Republic / Eiffel Tower and Seine River
-Italian Republic / Piazza dei Miracoli
-Kingdom of Spain / Abbey of Montserrat
-Kingdom of the Netherlands / Windmills at Kinderdijk
-Swiss Confederation / Matterhorn and Stellisee
-Republic of Poland / Tumski Bridge
-Kingdom of Sweden / Gamla stan
-Kingdom of Belgium / Flower Carpet at the Grand-Place
name: Landscapes with Flags of the World - Europe vol.1
